OL,3,CKing meets Jewish stabbing victims in
OL,4,Ca show of support for the community
OL,6,FThe King has met the Jewish victims of
OL,7,Fthe Golders Green stabbings in a show
OL,8,Fof support for the community.
OL,10,FCharles visited a Jewish Care charity
OL,11,Fcentre on Thursday to meet with
OL,12,Fvictims Shloime Rand, 34, and Moshe
OL,13,FBen Baila, 76, also known as Norman
OL,14,FShine, along with Chief Rabbi Sir
OL,15,FEphraim Mirvis and Metropolitan Police
OL,16,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley.
OL,18,FThe chief rabbi told the King they
OL,19,F"appreciate it enormously" that he had
OL,20,Fmade the visit.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@ZO]
