CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778854269
OL,3,CKing meets Jewish stabbing victims in
OL,4,Ca show of support for the community
OL,6,FCharles also spoke with members of the
OL,7,FJewish community police force Shomrim,
OL,8,Fwho were involved in responding to the
OL,9,Fattacks on April 29.
OL,11,FAfter speaking to the King, Mr Shine,
OL,12,Fwho was stabbed in the neck outside a
OL,13,Fbus stop during the attack, spoke
OL,14,Fabout the "genuine warmth" he had felt
OL,15,Ffrom the King.
OL,17,FHe said: "He was very concerned.
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@ZO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778854269
OL,3,CKing meets Jewish stabbing victims in
OL,4,Ca show of support for the community
OL,6,F"The most inspiring thing was that he
OL,7,Fdidn't let go of my hand, I mean it
OL,8,Fwas amazing, he is the King but I felt
OL,9,Fa genuine warmth and concern."
OL,11,FHe said that the visit felt "extremely
OL,12,Fimportant" for the whole Jewish
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,F"We feel we have a genuine friend in
OL,16,Fthe King," he added.
OL,18,FAfter meeting with the victims, the
OL,19,FKing greeted the crowds gathered
OL,20,Foutside the charity centre on Golders
OL,21,FGreen Road.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]sD@]OUtD@JO]wD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
