PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778854269
OL,3,CKing meets Jewish stabbing victims in
OL,4,Ca show of support for the community
OL,6,FHe waved to the crowds gathered
OL,7,Foutside and was greeted with chants of
OL,8,F"long live the King".
OL,10,FCharles shook hands with a man who
OL,11,Fturned 100 on Thursday.
OL,13,F"I hope they give you a good
OL,14,Fcelebration, and I hope you get a card
OL,15,Ffrom me," the King said.
OL,17,FHe was then presented with a loaf of
OL,18,Ftraditional Challah bread outside
OL,19,FGrodz bakery on the high street, and
OL,20,Fspoke to children from a local primary
OL,21,Fschool.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]uD@AOUwD@IO]
