OL,3,CKing meets Jewish stabbing victims in
OL,4,Ca show of support for the community
OL,6,FThe alleged Golders Green attacker
OL,7,FEssa Suleiman, 45, has been remanded
OL,8,Fin custody accused of three counts of
OL,9,Fattempted murder.
OL,11,FSuleiman is accused of trying to kill
OL,12,Fhis friend of 20 years, Ishmail
OL,13,FHussein at his home in Southwark
OL,14,Fbefore stabbing the two Jewish victims
OL,15,Fin the street on April 29.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
