OL,3,CKing meets Jewish stabbing victims in
OL,4,Ca show of support for the community
OL,6,FSuleiman was born in Somalia and came
OL,7,Fto the UK legally as a child in the
OL,8,F1990s, and was reported to Prevent,
OL,9,Fthe Government's anti-extremism
OL,10,Fprogramme, in 2020 but the case was
OL,11,Fclosed the same year.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
